#. Key:	EE0D4B944B1732FDBFEC1F9DF6554DB9
msgctxt ",EE0D4B944B1732FDBFEC1F9DF6554DB9"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>That's great to hear, you should get some rest. Tomorrow will be your first day. I'll call you at around 6 am, so make sure to be up by then.</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>听到你这么说真不错，你该休息一下了。明天就是你的第一天。我大概早上6点给你打电话，所以到时候一定要起床。</>"

#. Key:	69EC6CC949E0F344CBDFB79DE8F8B3E1
