msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah, thanks man, I really appreciate all the help. You know, honestly, I don't think I'd have made it this far without you.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>嗯，谢了兄弟，我真的很感谢你所有的帮助。说实话，我觉得没有你，我不可能撑到现在。</>"

