msgid "<Simon>Simon: </><Speech>Oh great, that's great. You know I really am proud of you actually committing to this part, you have made a lot of progress these last few months and just remember what we talked about and I know you will do great.</>"
msgstr "<Simon>Simon: </><Speech>哦太好了，真的太好了。你知道吗，我其实真的为你认真坚持到这一步感到骄傲。过去几个月你进步了很多，只要记得我们谈过的事，我知道你会做得很好。</>"

