msgctxt ",F7FFD2ED47F087F3F2369AB7F9E4E0AA"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah, that's right. But just one thing.. the gate. It wasn't locked. You haven't been over there have you?</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>对，没错。不过有一件事……那扇门。它没锁。你没去过那边吧？</>"

#. Key:	93E216A549C140134211CFADC03E200C
msgctxt ",93E216A549C140134211CFADC03E200C"
msgid "<Speech>Yeah, that's right.</>"
msgstr "<Speech>对，没错。</>"

#. Key:	D45D373346E7FE91327C7BA2A5244B0C
msgctxt ",D45D373346E7FE91327C7BA2A5244B0C"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Oh Clearwater! To the rescue, I'm guessing it was something wrong with the radio tower</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>哦 Clearwater！来救场了，我猜是无线电塔出了什么问题。</>"

#. Key:	845063914E8E9C3D05D235AA44A227FF
msgctxt ",845063914E8E9C3D05D235AA44A227FF"
msgid "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>Listen, we appreciate you saving the meeting today. But we don't have all the time in the world, so we need to get back to it. We'll take that later, so where was I...Ah yes, Animals...</>"
msgstr "<Rick>Rick: </><Speech>听着，我们感谢你今天挽救了会议。但我们没那么多时间，所以得继续。那件事之后再说，我刚才讲到哪了……啊对，动物……</>"

