msgstr "<Speech>好吧……</>"

#. Key:	F31E644B472B563EF85529AEB8CEFB16
msgctxt ",F31E644B472B563EF85529AEB8CEFB16"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>Listen man, I'm going out there again, I made it to the tower. I barely trail out there man, I'll just stay night here and first thing in the morning I'll continue hiking, alright?</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>听着兄弟，我不想再出去一次了，我已经到了塔。外面那条路几乎看不清，我今晚就住这里，明早第一件事继续徒步，好吗？</>"

#. Key:	2094363B4240C3B589692D811EADD831
msgctxt ",2094363B4240C3B589692D811EADD831"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah... go check if the generator down at the tower has any fuel and if it does just switch it on. And the lights should work.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>嗯……去看看塔下面的发电机有没有燃料，如果有就打开它。灯应该就能用了。</>"

#. Key:	9928C72E463AC25BC9ED74A3424992D8
msgctxt ",9928C72E463AC25BC9ED74A3424992D8"
msgid "<Speech>Yeah...</>"
msgstr "<Speech>嗯……</>"

