#. Key:	FF61C8794A5A9DECDF269898F4B814F2
msgctxt ",FF61C8794A5A9DECDF269898F4B814F2"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>I honestly don't know too much about it myself, but from what I've heard. He was there one day and then just gone... Not found yet</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>说实话，我自己知道的也不多，但我听说的是，他某天还在那里，然后就突然不见了……到现在还没找到。</>"

#. Key:	54CD271E4757F94E3A4EA9AD7C0960C5
msgctxt ",54CD271E4757F94E3A4EA9AD7C0960C5"
msgid "<Speech>I honestly don't know too much about it myself...</>"
msgstr "<Speech>说实话，我自己知道的也不多……</>"

#. Key:	149476DE4AD277C80FEB50A479784842
msgctxt ",149476DE4AD277C80FEB50A479784842"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>Missing? What do you mean?</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>失踪？什么意思？</>"

#. Key:	5509A39041073F606E2EE28C46B37A73
msgctxt ",5509A39041073F606E2EE28C46B37A73"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Yeah of course! Don't worry about it.</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>嗯，当然！别担心。</>"

#. Key:	DF2A841A4F02FBA8D0A459949AA3EC95
msgctxt ",DF2A841A4F02FBA8D0A459949AA3EC95"
msgid "<Speech>Yeah of course!</>"
msgstr "<Speech>嗯，当然！</>"

#. Key:	6C50920B4DF6EE238211C7A72D6C6DDA
msgctxt ",6C50920B4DF6EE238211C7A72D6C6DDA"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>Really!? Shit man... I don't really wanna go missing too, but you'll help me get out of here right?</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>真的！？该死兄弟……我可不想也失踪，但你会帮我离开这里，对吧？</>"

#. Key:	BCD1D286496B9D59FAC6CC8BAEE1C096
msgctxt ",BCD1D286496B9D59FAC6CC8BAEE1C096"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>That's a relief, thank you man</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>那我就放心了，谢谢兄弟。</>"

#. Key:	EF3B653249B41C030409CAAF545B8CCB
msgctxt ",EF3B653249B41C030409CAAF545B8CCB"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>Oh okay, I see...</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>哦好，我懂了……</>"

#. Key:	E0BEAB2C48E9C95F9EF1358E4AD80F8F
msgctxt ",E0BEAB2C48E9C95F9EF1358E4AD80F8F"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Cross road... Oh I see where you are, no need to worry about it. Just keep heading straight!</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>十字路口……哦，我知道你在哪了，不用担心。继续直走！</>"

#. Key:	0B92B245414A86D3BBF067B6EB3025B4
msgctxt ",0B92B245414A86D3BBF067B6EB3025B4"
msgid "<Speech>Just keep heading straight</>"
msgstr "<Speech>继续直走。</>"

#. Key:	96F02E5A4A604B4CE283189D162293E9
msgctxt ",96F02E5A4A604B4CE283189D162293E9"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Cross road... Oh I see where you are. Head to the opposite direction of the radio tower... so to your right! Should put you in the right direction</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>十字路口……哦，我知道你在哪了。往无线电塔相反的方向走……也就是你的右边！应该会带你走对方向。</>"

#. Key:	1607121C457853BD9A3FEC8B5490C1CC
msgctxt ",1607121C457853BD9A3FEC8B5490C1CC"
msgid "<Speech>If you head right it should put you in the right direction</>"
msgstr "<Speech>如果你往右走，应该就是正确方向。</>"

#. Key:	67D239624A8C011867BA18B6A44A8B15
msgctxt ",67D239624A8C011867BA18B6A44A8B15"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>So it's look like I reached a cross road. I think I see a trail that leds to a radio tower to my left. What should I do?</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>看起来我到了一个十字路口。我左边好像有条路通向无线电塔。我该怎么办？</>"

#. Key:	CAC0E9284E445A346F7937BC73DF2726
msgctxt ",CAC0E9284E445A346F7937BC73DF2726"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hey! I guess I'm not the only one out here</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>嘿！看来这里不只有我一个人。</>"

#. Key:	30F5F0D5494E74AF7B56E2ADF5A1A92C
msgctxt ",30F5F0D5494E74AF7B56E2ADF5A1A92C"
msgid "<Speech>You're the lookout over by the lake?</>"
msgstr "<Speech>你就是湖边那个瞭望员？</>"

#. Key:	970931124391A9B6149277A755A4A591
msgctxt ",970931124391A9B6149277A755A4A591"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Well... I think it's great that the flowers are gonna pull through</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>嗯……我觉得那些花能活下来真不错。</>"

#. Key:	725B254F4A57C79BEA1FF990CE29C1AB
msgctxt ",725B254F4A57C79BEA1FF990CE29C1AB"
msgid "<Speech>I think it's great that the flowers are gonna make it</>"
msgstr "<Speech>我觉得那些花能活下来真不错。</>"

#. Key:	BD8967FA469463E52D7A8FB342EF9924
msgctxt ",BD8967FA469463E52D7A8FB342EF9924"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Hey, um..I'm the new lookout over at Clearwater</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>嘿，嗯……我是 Clearwater 的新瞭望员。</>"

#. Key:	84645C1146CBDED1298612A7DAF012AC
msgctxt ",84645C1146CBDED1298612A7DAF012AC"
msgid "<Speech>I'm the new lookout over at Clearwater</>"
msgstr "<Speech>我是 Clearwater 的新瞭望员。</>"

