msgctxt ",72C7539A4F78979C231F9189C0C863B2"
msgid "<Speech>Then you should head to the left!</>"
msgstr "<Speech>那你应该往左边！</>"

#. Key:	94BF49E246979262D40F5C88B7453B92
msgctxt ",94BF49E246979262D40F5C88B7453B92"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>Yep</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>没错。</>"

#. Key:	BC3547AF4A4ACAF9CBD0A39C03C2C46B
msgctxt ",BC3547AF4A4ACAF9CBD0A39C03C2C46B"
msgid "<Hiker>Hiker: </><Speech>Left...Alright!</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>徒步者: </><Speech>左边……好！</>"

#. Key:	CE8108A74765774B6552AEBBBCB908DE
msgctxt ",CE8108A74765774B6552AEBBBCB908DE"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Just keep heading forward and you'll get to the exit of the park. You'll see a cross road later but just keep going forward</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>一直往前走，你就会到公园出口。之后你会看到一个十字路口，但继续往前走就行。</>"

#. Key:	EE2065814876E46A7EDC55A6714BA634
msgctxt ",EE2065814876E46A7EDC55A6714BA634"
msgid "<Speech>Just keep heading forward and you'll get to the exit of the park.</>"
msgstr "<Speech>一直往前走，你就会到公园出口。</>"

#. Key:	013E9625479988387461A9A84F3F37E5
msgctxt ",013E9625479988387461A9A84F3F37E5"
msgid "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>Honestly, take the left path. It will lead you to my tower, I think it's better you don't stay out there any longer. You can just continue tomorrow when it's light out</>"
msgstr "<Sam>Sam: </><Speech>说真的，走左边那条路。它会带你到我的塔，我觉得你不要再继续待在外面比较好。明天天亮后你再继续也行。</>"

