msgctxt ",90D345054391BD4F8EA1FFAAAF1642FB"
msgid "<Hiker>Park Ranger: </><Speech>Scared you didn't I? But, what are you doing out here anyway? You lost or something?</>"
msgstr "<Hiker>护林员: </><Speech>我吓到你了，对吧？不过你到底在外面干什么？迷路了还是怎样？</>"

